data.description: Picturesque cottage-style home, completely move-in ready & filled w/modern amenities! This charming home boasts newer metal roof, brand new HVAC & hot water tank, ensuring worry-free living for years to come. Newer windows flood the home w/natural light, highlighting the stunning hardwood floors that flow throughout most of the home. Beautiful kitchen, complete w/pantry space and & the modern countertops. The main floor features primary bedroom for added convenience, along with a dedicated laundry room. Second level houses cute secondary bedroom w/optional third bedroom, currently utilized as an expansive closet, offering flexibility to suit your needs. Outside find your private oasis—a relaxing rear deck w/pergola, perfect for enjoying morning coffee or hosting gatherings. The oversized double lot offers over .25 acres, providing plenty of space for outdoor activities. Additional storage space available in unfinished basement area, outdoor shed, & additional off street parking in the rear parking pad!
